{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950570/extras/_img_desc.png?t=1612333846\" /><br>Collect bits to grow your worm \u2014 but don't bite your tail! Outwit (and out-eat) an army of hungry ants and fast-moving centipedes in this challenging, 8-bit quarter game. <br><br>Bitworm is a throwback to classic arcade games of yesteryear, complete with retro graphics and 8-bit sound tones. In this alteration of the classic Snake game, you work to grow your worm by obtaining bits while avoiding running into ants. <br><br>Work quickly to eliminate all of the ants in each stage to progress to the next stage. If an ant eats a bit, it may spawn a new ant! If you take too long to clear a stage, more ants will spawn!<br><br>The longer you grow your worm's tail, the easier it will be to trick ants into hitting you, but don't bite your tail! Biting your own tail will spawn a centipede! Centipedes move as fast as you do, and can grow up to 50 segments long! They are also smart enough to avoid running into your worm!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950570/extras/_img_bwrmGIF.gif?t=1612333846\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950570/extras/_img_add.png?t=1612333846\" /><br>If the current game is too difficult for you, you can type &quot;<i><strong>EXTRALIFE</strong></i>&quot; on the main menu to start the next game with an extra life. Entering &quot;<i><strong>TOOEASY</strong></i>&quot; on the main menu will unlock an extra hard difficulty mode!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/950570/extras/_img_badges.png?t=1612333846\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"One for One","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/950570/b0e54202194a9b91ebf698e6163b71b397102ec